name: 8 bit video game pop
code:
stack(
  s("bd*2 sd*2").gain(0.8),
  s("hh*4").gain(0.5),
  note("<c4 d4 e4 g4>").s("square").cutoff(700).decay(0.3).gain(0.7),
  note("<e4 g4 b4 c5>").s("sawtooth").cutoff(600).decay(0.2).gain(0.6)
)

name: 8 bit cat
code:
stack(
  s("bd hh sd hh [cp ~ cp] hh").fast(2).gain(0.8),
  note("<c2 g2 e3 c3>").s("square").slow(2).gain(0.7),
  note("<c4 d4 e4 g4>").s("sawtooth").fast(4).gain(0.9),
  note("<e3 g3 c4>").s("triangle").gain(0.6),
  note("c5").s("sine").slow(4).gain(0.4)
)

name: angelic soft synth
code:
stack(
  note("<c4 e4 g4 b4> <g4 c5 e5> <a4 e5 g5> <f4 a4 c5>").spread().fast(4).s("triangle").gain(0.84).room(0.85).decay(1.55),
  note("<c3 g3 e4> <a3 e4 c4>").s("sine").gain(0.4).room(0.8).decay(1.2).slow(2)
)

name: goth melodic house
code:
stack(
  s("bd*4").gain(0.9).decay(0.08),
  s("~ cp ~ cp").gain(0.7).decay(0.1).room(0.1),
  s("hh ~ hh ~ hh hh ~ hh").fast(2).gain(0.4).decay(0.05).pan("<0.2 0.8>"),
  note("c2 g1 a1 f1").s("sawtooth").gain(0.7).decay(0.6).cutoff(350).room(0.1),
  note("<c3 eb3 g3 bb3> <d3 f3 a3 c4> <eb3 g3 bb3 d4> <c3 eb3 g3 bb3>").s("square").gain(0.5).decay(1.5).room(0.7).cutoff(600).slow(0.5),
  note("g4 eb4 c4 bb3 f4 d4 c4 eb4").s("triangle").gain(0.6).decay(0.2).room(0.1).cutoff(1200).fast(1.5)
)

name: looping angelic cathedral synt...
description: looping angelic cathedral synth inspired by andrea bocelli
code:
stack(
  note("<c5 e5 g5> <g5 b5 d6> <a5 c6 e6> <f5 a5 c6>")
    .s("triangle")
    .slow(0.5)
    .gain(0.09)
    .decay(0.55)
    .room(0.65),
  note("<c6 e6 g6> <d6 g6 b6> <e6 g6 c7> <f6 a6 c7>")
    .s("sine")
    .slow(0.5)
    .gain(0.11)
    .decay(2)
    .room(0.8)
    .pan(range(0.2, 0.8, 0.2))
)
